# setURI:

**Article**

Sets the URI of the receiver.

## Overview

The receiver must be an [doc://com.apple.foundation/documentation/Foundation/XMLElement] or [doc://com.apple.foundation/documentation/Foundation/XMLDocument] document, or an attribute (that is, an`NSXMLNode` object of type [doc://com.apple.foundation/documentation/Foundation/XMLNode/Kind-swift.enum/attribute]). For documents it is the URI of document origin.
